<sp/><sp/>}
<sp/><sp/>///start<sp/>the<sp/>daily<sp/>mission<sp/>at<sp/>hh:mm<sp/>today<sp/>or<sp/>tomorrow
<sp/><sp/>QDate<sp/>date<sp/>=<sp/>QDate::currentDate();
<sp/>if<sp/>(QTime::currentTime().msecsTo(QTime(hh,<sp/>mm,<sp/>00,<sp/>000))<sp/>&lt;=<sp/>0)<sp/>{<sp/>//if<sp/>the<sp/>current<sp/>time<sp/>is<sp/>after<sp/>12:00,
